  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<section id=\"null\" class=\"secret\"><p>When applied to the skin of a creature, the creature must succeed on a DC 22 Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, the creature can't use reactions, its speed is halved, and it can't make more than one attack on its turn. In addition, the creature can use either an action or a bonus action on its turn, but not both. These effects last for 1 minute. The creature can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself with a successful save. Can be mastercrafted (alchemist's supplies) into a Potion of Polymorph (allows the drinker to change shape as though they had cast the Polymorph spell).</p></section>",
